================================================================================================
Lazervida fw v1.0.1 (20221228)
* Change
    * Changed the sensitivity of tilt detect (~20degree) and reduced noise with software filter
* Fix
    * Fixed incorrect laser power in fast raster engraving
    * Fixed stop unexpectedly
* 更改
    * 增加傾斜偵測靈敏度, 並降低六軸加速度計雜訊
* 修正
    * 修正快速雕刻的雷射出光強度偏低問題與條紋問題
    * 修正未預期停止問題
================================================================================================
Lazervida fw v0.1.5 (20220921)
* Change
    * Increase the sampling for G-sensor to mitigate vibration noise during motion
    * Changed tilt detection threshold to 35 degree
* 更改
    * 增加加速儀取樣數量, 降低機器運作過程的震動造成的數值誤差
    * 更改傾斜偵測角度為35度
================================================================================================
Lazervida fw v0.1.4 (20220921)
* Change
    * Enabled tilt detection with threshold of 20 degree
* 更改
    * 開啟傾斜偵測,傾斜角達20度自動暫停
================================================================================================
Lazervida fw v0.1.3 (20220913)
* Change
    * Lowered the sensitivity of collision detect to reduce the chance of misdetection
* 更改
    * 降低碰撞偵測的靈敏度, 減少誤判
================================================================================================
Lazervida fw v0.1.2 (20220831)
* Fix
    * Fixed incorrect position state when initial automatic homing failed
* 修正
    * 修正初始歸零失敗後,系統位置為負值,觸發軟體限位
================================================================================================
Lazervida fw v0.1.1 (20220822)
* Change
    * Disable tilt detection
* 更改
    * 關閉傾斜偵測
